%U A394192 23695,26252,28987,31906,35015,38320,41827,45542,49471,53620,57995,62602,67447,72536,77875,83470
%N A394192 a(n) = n^3 - n^2 + 5*n + 2.
%D A394192 Murray R. Spiegel, Calculus of Finite Differences and Difference Equations, "Schaum's Outline Series", McGraw-Hill, 1971, exercise 2.8 on page 43.
%H A394192 <a href="/index/Rec#order_04">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, signature (4,-6,4,-1).
%F A394192 a(n) = 4*a(n-1) - 6*a(n-2) + 4*a(n-3) - a(n-4) for n > 3.
%F A394192 G.f.: (2 - x + 5*x^3)/(1 - x)^4.
%F A394192 E.g.f.: exp(x)*(2 + 5*x + 2*x^2 + x^3).
%t A394192 a[n_]:=n^3-n^2+5n+2; Array[a,45,0]
